{"tid":1163754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯修訂條例—白宮聯署 幫手推上熱門","createTime":"2019-05-20T15:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T22:53:46.000Z","uid":214734,"like":102,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea8c69e6ae0eaec17c9453dbd000ec30de8d625","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"我見到香港小國民巴打既post 好似冇上到熱門 冇咁多人見到 而家再開 求大家幫幫手簽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接上個post <br />\n小弟尋日喺We the People網站發起左聯署<br />\n要求華府就逃犯條例嘅修訂表示反對，並且審視現時美國同香港嘅逃犯引渡協議<br />\n希望各位巴打絲打一齊參與呢個聯署<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=717ac8d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n個聯署因為係尋晚比較臨時臨急寫嘅，同埋因為字數限制，所以本來想寫要求華府考慮係咪暫停實施《美國&mdash;香港政策法》都無寫到落去<br />\n不過希望大家都可以簽下呢個聯署<br />\n至少做多一樣嘢，希望令到國際社會盡快表態反對<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思我講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然一開始好多人都收唔到確認email，但尋晚起越嚟越多人開始收到。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjMTq5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjMTq5B.png&h=e5ec8270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手簽之餘，可以share 埋比身邊嘅人，唔知發生緊乜事嘅就解釋佢哋聽，等多啲人知道。 <br />\n簽個名唔係好難姐，希望大家真係幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8Y23Sm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8Y23Sm.png&h=fd31daf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b3628a3fdced38a26fa2fe53251a84f9add8107","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dda5ea7c6de074d89d54efd935bcda0073da495","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ee7e44257df282ab0a2ae32af72c8cd078b7b6f","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c0712bd34e8ac6087132cbbba7b7a0dea8cd839","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3608e5dd9197246e105266b4743dbce678c9676a","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ede23a3cb88247e41d6172fda3bbf4fffcc4d1e","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bb284bf9c1bf8979f95c470a8246de1af913d1e","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c061d46d0d432a91ebe10e064ccbf978f50d456","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d67a11b51dd30c289bd116f5ae7d2dff661f359e","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手推post"},{"pid":"bc04768fcf0ce3a8bd2a4da4c6a3902a1f412fea","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"701d29d8bf41a0b549ac1c68e7e7acd738023014","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手推post"},{"pid":"eb9d2b0de8b9e310a49ea1a747592b0dc3b2fb05","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手推post"},{"pid":"89a7c35f0c3c6af34371529f99177e28a551f3c8","tid":1163754,"uid":214734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"