sg":"推"},{"pid":"54d7460136cc4e64c3dcde107964e361176cae79","tid":1163754,"uid":102347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"香港人幾時醒<br />\n就以4000蚊為例子<br />\n全香港人都比陳茂波條撚樣撚到香港人<br />\n點解今時今日仲未有人叫條垃圾落台？<br />\n其他國家一早已經出黎遊行叫條陳茂波拎返個位出黎<br />\n點解香港人仲要受條撚樣氣<br />\n果4000蚊 唔係政府架<br />\n係我地班納稅人架<br />\n點解我地唔出黎抵抗 <br />\n叫佢加快腳步？ <br />\n佢咁少事都做唔黎<br />\n香港人既錢點交比呢個人？<br />\n派錢都派唔到<br />\n咁不如叫佢讓個位出黎比其他人做<br />\n我唔信全港人企出黎<br />\n叫佢落台 我唔信無效<br />\n我地一直比人恰到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8fd79bb30fcfd35f40740ee0f7feb549280198","tid":1163754,"uid":18370,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"其實簽完有乜用？<br />\n次次簽完都好似無左下文？<br />\n係咪好似facebook 果啲集氣咁樣..."},{"pid":"0638a8457b5238fe812d9fd7e4046c734c3debb5","tid":1163754,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc243015786f0d967114419c958b59681cd43edb","tid":1163754,"uid":41428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"簽咗，推"},{"pid":"227191078010e1a068628e78543d4fe04319cdbf","tid":1163754,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ad08809f2e9223ac492443660d1b8387ae3af2","tid":1163754,"uid":199244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T19:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d89c24b4f27c5395c6276dc4e1675639d67483","tid":1163754,"uid":142651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T19:39:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9004af786f234904bb1b33563f49d19e004877a7","tid":1163754,"uid":209781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T19:45:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80c28417e48e9d51c7161fed6ec6062063820caa","tid